                            <div class="divider"></div>
                            <p>Instrumentation is the central part of our CubeSat. The first part of our instrument selection process asks what part of the electromagnetic spectrum you would like to observe. The spectrum is divided into five distinct regions, based on the energy production mechanisms, detection methods, and analysis techniques. These will be explained further on the page. After you choose a region, we will narrow down the parts capable of working with the associated wavelength, as well as the scale of process you will be able to observe.</p>
